# Rust
/target
**/target
Cargo.lock.bak
*.rs.bk
# Project-scoped Rust toolchain (RUSTUP_HOME / CARGO_HOME live here — never machine-wide).
# See CONTRIBUTING.md "Development setup". This directory is large (~1.2 GB) and local-only.
/.toolchain/
# direnv (optional local activation of the project-scoped toolchain)
/.direnv/
.env
.envrc.local
# Fuzzing
/fuzz/target
/fuzz/corpus
/fuzz/artifacts
/vendor/
# Coverage
*.profraw
/coverage
# Vault runtime artifacts — NEVER commit a real vault or its local state
*.vlt
*.vlt.bak
*.state
.vault.toml
# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
# Secrets — defense in depth; nothing secret should ever live in-tree
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
# Private development methodology + per-feature research/patterns ("secret sauce").
# The shippable outputs (specs in docs/, PRD, code) are public; the process is not.
/.sdlc/
